#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.104"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.104:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.104:0.2"
msgid "11. Valāhakavagga "
msgstr "11. Clouds "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.104:0.3"
msgid "104. Udakarahadasutta "
msgstr "104. Lakes "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.104:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, udakarahadā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four lakes. "

msgctxt "an4.104:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><ol>
msgctxt "an4.104:1.3"
msgid "Uttāno gambhīrobhāso, gambhīro uttānobhāso, uttāno uttānobhāso, gambhīro gambhīrobhāso—"
msgstr "~One is shallow but appears deep, ~one is deep but appears shallow, ~one is shallow and appears shallow, and ~one is deep and appears deep. "

#. HTML: </ol><p>
msgctxt "an4.104:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro udakarahadā. "
msgstr "These are the four lakes. "

msgctxt "an4.104:1.5"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, cattāro udakarahadūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "In the same way, these four people similar to lakes are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an4.104:1.6"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><ol>
msgctxt "an4.104:1.7"
msgid "Uttāno gambhīrobhāso, gambhīro uttānobhāso, uttāno uttānobhāso, gambhīro gambhīrobhāso. "
msgstr "~One is shallow but appears deep, ~one is deep but appears shallow, ~one is shallow and appears shallow, and ~one is deep and appears deep. "

#. HTML: </ol><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.104:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo uttāno hoti gambhīrobhāso? "
msgstr "And how is a person shallow but appears deep? "

msgctxt "an4.104:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ paṭikkantaṃ ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a person is impressive when going out and coming back, when looking ahead and aside, when bending and extending the limbs, and when bearing the outer robe, bowl and robes. "

msgctxt "an4.104:2.3"
msgid "So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "But they don’t really understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’. "

msgctxt "an4.104:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo uttāno hoti gambhīrobhāso. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is shallow but appears deep. "

msgctxt "an4.104:2.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, udakarahado uttāno gambhīrobhāso; "
msgstr "That person is like a lake that’s shallow but appears deep, I say. "

msgctxt "an4.104:2.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.106, sc3
msgctxt "an4.104:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo gambhīro hoti uttānobhāso? "
msgstr "And how is a person deep but appears shallow? "

msgctxt "an4.104:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa na pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ paṭikkantaṃ ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a person is not impressive … "

msgctxt "an4.104:3.3"
msgid "So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "But they really understand: ‘This is suffering’ … "

msgctxt "an4.104:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo gambhīro hoti uttānobhāso. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.104:3.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, udakarahado gambhīro uttānobhāso; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.104:3.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.104:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo uttāno hoti uttānobhāso? "
msgstr "And how is a person shallow and appears shallow? "

msgctxt "an4.104:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa na pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ paṭikkantaṃ ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a person is not impressive … "

msgctxt "an4.104:4.3"
msgid "So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
msgstr "Nor do they really understand: ‘This is suffering’ … "

msgctxt "an4.104:4.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo uttāno hoti uttānobhāso. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.104:4.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, udakarahado uttāno uttānobhāso; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.104:4.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.104:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo gambhīro hoti gambhīrobhāso? "
msgstr "And how is a person deep and appears deep? "

msgctxt "an4.104:5.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ paṭikkantaṃ ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a person is impressive … "

msgctxt "an4.104:5.3"
msgid "So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "And they really understand: ‘This is suffering’ … "

msgctxt "an4.104:5.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo gambhīro hoti gambhīrobhāso. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.104:5.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, udakarahado gambhīro gambhīrobhāso; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.104:5.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.104:5.7"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro udakarahadūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti. "
msgstr "These four people similar to lakes are found in the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.104:5.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

